能力走既都走左<br />\n<br />\n有鬥志既坐左監<br />\n<br />\n餘下既只為私利內鬥，互暗互篤<br />\n<br />\n香港主權已經係中國，班廢中廢老都反唔到主權移交<br />\n<br />\n而家先識驚？末期癌症先諗方法？<br />\n<br />\n以為啲旁門左道有用，乜乜隱世神醫，最後錢都洗曬又係死，人唔吠狗都笑"},{"pid":"c1308955acb732dea5d7ae1b36f830f2aa58dbfd","tid":1170082,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad6f4d8c00a3d5632a613e3899286b434b5537f","tid":1170082,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我身邊有去雨革既fd都唔理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"其實我都明白<br />\n佔中之後就咩嘢都無<br />\n普選個啲 不了了之<br />\n無咩人再提 個種無力感咁大<br />\n<br />\n加上啲集會又好無組織<br />\n完左除左有人數 有一個紀錄<br />\n仲會唔會有其他嘢<br />\n<br />\n始終都差咁個人/組織<br />\n可以凝聚一大班人<br />\n可以帶領大家做一啲改變<br />\n<br />\n當呢個時勢<br />\n你做啲浮面啲嘅人 就好快比人搞<br />\n仲有邊個會做"},{"pid":"786d95faa076e759b7468251b622101443b5314a","tid":1170082,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"有，仲要BC、英國大學畢業<br />\n但支持起高鐵、覺得你乖共產黨就唔搞你<br />\n鬼唔望之後比人抄家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1463f693314ccf602a264f8fa7d5de8d92834d0","tid":1170082,"uid":255216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T20:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c00432ce1c71ec5d4930021b750fbe8ca778ca","tid":1170082,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:26:50.000Z","msg":"老豆老母唔理呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413f0427c2475fd3727bf1c0d38d1b0091159e72","tid":1170082,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1308955acb732dea5d7ae1b36f830f2aa58dbfd","tid":1170082,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad6f4d8c00a3d5632a613e3899286b434b5537f","tid":1170082,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:08:06.000Z",